---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" lang="en">
  <section class="pt-12 pb-20 lg:pt-16 lg:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">
          About <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-500">EMPAT Solutions</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-cyan-500 rounded"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        
        <div class="text-slate-300 space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p class="font-medium text-white text-xl border-l-4 border-cyan-500 pl-4">
            My name is Dr. Eng. Emil Patelski. I am the founder and CEO of EMPAT Solutions. My passion lies in bridging the gap between scientific rigor, modern business dynamics, and advanced technologies.
          </p>
          <p>
            My journey into the world of Artificial Intelligence began in academia. After earning my Ph.D. at the Poznań University of Life Sciences, where I researched innovative technologies, I decided to bring my analytical, research-oriented, and—most importantly—empathetic approach to the digital realm.
          </p>
          <p>
            At EMPAT Solutions, I help businesses and scientific institutions understand and effectively leverage AI. I specialize in training and consulting focused on process automation, data analysis, customer service, and modern marketing. My goal is to translate complex technology into measurable, tangible benefits, tailoring the scope of cooperation to the unique needs of your organization.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our Operational Vectors</h3>
	   <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg width="32" height="32" class="w-8 h-8 shrink-0 text-cyan-400 mr-4 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-white block">Security-First Approach</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Every AI solution is deployed maintaining the highest data protection standards.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg width="32" height="32" class="w-8 h-8 shrink-0 text-cyan-400 mr-4 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-white block">Operational Efficiency</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">We automate processes, reducing costs and execution time for mission-critical tasks.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg width="32" height="32" class="w-8 h-8 shrink-0 text-cyan-400 mr-4 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <strong class="text-white block">Tailored Solutions</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">We flexibly adapt the scope of training to the specific needs of each organization.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
